room_title: Escape room "The Classroom" by Rooms of No Return in Bakersfield
room_description: You have entered Ms. Ana's classroom. She's a psychopath who fancies kidnapping people. Torturing and pretending they are her students is her obsession. Many have tried to escape her madness but have failed, and now she has kidnapped you and taken you to her secret room. Its now your turn to find your way out! You will have 1 hour to find your way out before Ms. Ana returns from lunch.
